{"tid":47163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG admin入 （for 肥婆emoji)","createTime":"2016-12-20T07:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T12:37:02.000Z","uid":12628,"like":61,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a285bff964fa6b7e1cd2b197aca22bdf6f903121","tid":47163,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/150709_b9bd0d6861636f4ac258b7bdced13ba2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F150709_b9bd0d6861636f4ac258b7bdced13ba2.jpg&h=80563836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論你保留定刪走個emoji, 都會有人反對。<br />\n根本無可能滿足所有人既要求，亦無需要咁做。<br />\n作為創作人，你地應該堅持自己既創作理念，我上得呢個論壇，就係對你地既支持！<br />\n所以，所以，所以，無論你地留定刪個emoji, 只要你地落左決定，我就會尊重。<br />\n希望肥婆emoji呢件事就此完結，唔好令辛辛苦苦為大家創作呢個咁可貴地方既admin難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5139645a4a73034f45967b1f41a343857f9d6d73","tid":47163,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"67c83a8ddaa681a44cb8cf44ae9b09819d62a852","tid":47163,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba58af66eba777e9429cd815ec6989471beda44d","tid":47163,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29c38be62cd93c5b5d30401073fb3849a5a93cf","tid":47163,"uid":67400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"依啲咪叫高汁#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"b0dc632e1601f39ce0e3d114d2ee982f78742ee0","tid":47163,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/