<br />\n最撚簡單，admin整個公投留定刪，咁都唔識做？"},{"pid":"6c84b223a9db314bb92c427aee4d86590f966aba","tid":47163,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甘見到5P字記得吾好屌牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本兩樣嘢，唔好撈埋嚟講，你手殘腦殘唔識打字就走去學識打字先，或者請移玉步去5P！！<br />\n<br />\n都唔知肥婆icon同5P字有咩關？不嬲高登仔去到而家連登仔都係恥笑肥婆㗎啦，其實幾啱連登仔用添！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"0ddfa6ecd5bc837ebd2463f4ccb6618668ca86fe","tid":47163,"uid":616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實個問題係：套icon真係好撚核突，仲要做埋official icon，等人咁易用到嗰吓先攞命。而家班5p仔，淨係識用icon洗版，你老母你試吓去任何一個post都見撚到小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呀，你反唔反胃呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果有一日有人講話腦魔icon好樣衰，咁係咪應該唔要腦魔icon??<br />\n<br />\n同埋，人地一擔心機整多D icon出嚟，你唔鐘意咪唔好用囉，但你地咁樣咪即係間接扼殺創意，咁其他人有新橋想整新icon,咪要考慮埋會唔會比人屌㗎等等，咁仲有咩人會攪新嘢？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你d盲撐撚仲未明個問題所在<br />\n<br />\n而家admin就係好似個垃圾政府咁假諮詢（自己開圍爐post多正評）<br />\n<br />\n根本大部份人都無入過個post同意擺set icon做官方icon，就當左好多人支持，而家反對嗰d就無野搵野黎嘈，都係嗰句，admin而家set個公投，多人支持佢咪留囉，點解要逼其他人陪你地一齊食屎"},{"pid":"b99c8b930a70a4d84b3feee45292d6ab62bc41bb"